---
title: Golden Parmesan Pork Schnitzels with Bacon-Cherry Tomato Salad & Smokey Aioli
description: It’s that time of the week, schnitty night! We’ve been looking forward to showing off this one. A sharp cheesy crumb coats tender pork to transform it into the ultimate schnitzel. Add a dollop of smokey aioli for a flavourful finish.
